1
00:01:15,700 --> 00:01:20,940
=About Love=

2
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,940
=Episode 9=

3
00:01:54,150 --> 00:01:55,870
Did you call these people over today?

4
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,510
What people?

5
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,150
Is there some misunderstanding?

6
00:01:59,710 --> 00:02:00,790
Just spit it out.

7
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:04,120
I haven't seen you in ages,
so I miss you so much.

8
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,870
And I'm dying to know

9
00:02:06,400 --> 00:02:07,590
what kind of

10
00:02:07,590 --> 00:02:08,960
boyfriend you got?

11
00:02:13,040 --> 00:02:14,590
I'll bring him to meet you
in a couple of days.

12
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,400
That sounds great.

13
00:02:16,470 --> 00:02:18,520
I've been free lately. Come anytime.

14
00:02:32,300 --> 00:02:36,820
(Bei)

15
00:02:38,280 --> 00:02:39,630
Are you gonna call him?

16
00:02:44,030 --> 00:02:45,960
You wanna tell him everything about me?

17
00:02:47,150 --> 00:02:48,120
Think carefully.

18
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,710
He might be at
another woman's place right now.

19
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:58,000
Do you really think
he can understand me?

20
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,710
Do you even know him that well?

21
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,430
Who is he calling today?

22
00:03:07,890 --> 00:03:08,730
It's already so late.

23
00:03:08,750 --> 00:03:10,000
Why does he have to go see her?

24
00:03:11,590 --> 00:03:13,150
Do you know his past?

25
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,240
Tell me,

26
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:17,240
will he be just like other guys?

27
00:03:18,400 --> 00:03:20,120
Stop dodging my question. Look at me.

28
00:03:21,590 --> 00:03:22,840
Look at me!

29
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:26,910
Before you figure out
who he's actually meeting,

30
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,630
don't tell him anything.

31
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:29,870
Most importantly,

32
00:03:30,120 --> 00:03:31,240
never let anyone

33
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:33,030
tell him about me.

34
00:03:37,300 --> 00:03:40,060
(Bei)

35
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,960
Don't hesitate.

36
00:04:07,430 --> 00:04:08,590
Hello, Guan.

37
00:04:10,430 --> 00:04:11,590
Let's make it tonight.

38
00:04:12,750 --> 00:04:14,470
Do you two keep in touch privately?

39
00:04:15,190 --> 00:04:16,560
Only when necessary.

40
00:04:16,750 --> 00:04:17,800
I got nothing to hide.

41
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:19,360
Then why not tell Bei?

42
00:04:19,710 --> 00:04:20,550
Do I need to check in

43
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,870
with Xiu when I shop with you?

44
00:04:22,070 --> 00:04:23,190
You're no different from me.

45
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,750
Shoving our own logic

46
00:04:24,830 --> 00:04:25,950
down others' throats.

47
00:04:26,360 --> 00:04:28,510
The difference between us is

48
00:04:29,830 --> 00:04:31,720
I know how to follow my heart

49
00:04:31,830 --> 00:04:32,920
without crossing lines.

50
00:04:40,300 --> 00:04:41,540
(Jiang Yifan)

51
00:04:45,800 --> 00:04:46,640
Hello.

52
00:04:47,390 --> 00:04:49,390
Got any plans tonight?

53
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:52,160
Yeah.

54
00:04:53,310 --> 00:04:54,310
Just kidding.

55
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:56,560
Silly, I'll go with your plan.

56
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,070
Can you come over?

57
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,650
Sure.

58
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,600
Wait for me.

59
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,030
Her?

60
00:05:04,390 --> 00:05:05,230
Ah.

61
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:07,760
Go on then.

62
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:17,310
Do you think having a kindred person

63
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,800
makes you less lonely?

64
00:05:19,070 --> 00:05:20,120
I don't need one.

65
00:05:20,220 --> 00:05:21,240
Besides, things like this.

66
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,870
No one can ease this guilt of mine.

67
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:25,480
I just enjoy seeing people fall in love.

68
00:05:25,950 --> 00:05:27,630
No matter who. No matter what bond.

69
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:30,600
Then I might let you down.

70
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,960
Stop pretending.

71
00:05:32,360 --> 00:05:33,430
I know you're in love.

72
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:35,070
This is the kind of love you want.

73
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:36,720
Crazy.

74
00:05:37,190 --> 00:05:39,190
Take care of my little fairy. Bye.

75
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,360
Mingming.

76
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:45,070
Turn your body a little.

77
00:06:45,570 --> 00:06:46,560
No need to lift your head.

78
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:48,200
Yeah.

79
00:06:51,240 --> 00:06:52,360
Hold on.

80
00:06:54,040 --> 00:06:54,920
I think we're

81
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,270
moving too fast, aren't we?

82
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:57,670
Not really.

83
00:06:58,160 --> 00:06:59,680
We're officially a couple now.

84
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:01,390
Yeah.

85
00:07:01,510 --> 00:07:02,430
But I still feel...

86
00:07:02,800 --> 00:07:03,750
a little nervous.

87
00:07:03,760 --> 00:07:04,600
I came here planning to

88
00:07:04,610 --> 00:07:05,560
give myself to you,

89
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,400
but

90
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:07,590
I think maybe we

91
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,480
need to get closer.

92
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,950
Aren't we close enough already?

93
00:07:10,390 --> 00:07:11,230
Mingming,

94
00:07:11,270 --> 00:07:13,160
we're officially together today.

95
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,870
Relax, okay?

96
00:07:15,480 --> 00:07:16,750
Just give me a bit more time.

97
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,480
I've already given you so much.

98
00:07:18,920 --> 00:07:19,760
Mingming,

99
00:07:19,950 --> 00:07:21,190
I really like you.

100
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,390
Sen, stop!

101
00:07:23,580 --> 00:07:24,750
Keep going, and I'll get mad.

102
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:25,950
Why?

103
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,920
You're the one who asked for it tonight.

104
00:07:28,500 --> 00:07:29,510
It'll be quick, Mingming.

105
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,950
Sen, Sen!

106
00:07:39,240 --> 00:07:40,680
Are... are you okay?

107
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:42,720
You're still thinking about him, right?

108
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:45,510
I'm not.

109
00:07:47,310 --> 00:07:48,750
I know I can't compare to him.

110
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,270
I know girls only give themselves
to someone they love.

111
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:53,070
Whether you're their boyfriend or not.

112
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:53,960
Don't say that.

113
00:07:54,430 --> 00:07:55,720
Did I say something wrong?

114
00:07:56,620 --> 00:07:58,000
Honestly, I'm just jealous of him.

115
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,870
He's already
taken over your heart completely.

116
00:08:00,630 --> 00:08:01,800
You wanted it with him.

117
00:08:01,970 --> 00:08:03,750
But when I touch you,
everything feels off.

118
00:08:03,830 --> 00:08:05,310
It's not like that.

119
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:07,870
He respected me at first.

120
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,950
When we were in bed…

121
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,630
Don't talk about that!

122
00:08:24,390 --> 00:08:25,600
Stop messing around, okay?

123
00:08:27,720 --> 00:08:29,390
Today's our first official day together.

124
00:08:29,510 --> 00:08:31,510
I don't wanna fight over this.

125
00:08:33,510 --> 00:08:34,350
Sorry.

126
00:08:36,200 --> 00:08:37,630
I didn't respect you enough.

127
00:08:38,670 --> 00:08:39,670
I apologize.

128
00:08:39,830 --> 00:08:40,720
Sen.

129
00:08:40,840 --> 00:08:41,790
You… you sleep first.

130
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:43,630
I'll… I'll wait in the living room.

131
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,480
Hello.

132
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:07,240
Have we met before?

133
00:09:09,200 --> 00:09:10,080
Who are you?

134
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,000
I'm your husband.

135
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,840
From another parallel universe.

136
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:15,080
We have two cute daughters.

137
00:09:15,200 --> 00:09:16,270
And a pet dog.

138
00:09:16,510 --> 00:09:18,720
One day,
you left home with just a letter behind.

139
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:19,840
You said the world's vast.

140
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:22,320
And you wanted to find a lamppost.

141
00:09:22,340 --> 00:09:23,480
Why are you dressed like this?

142
00:09:24,150 --> 00:09:25,630
Didn't you tell me to dress formally?

143
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:26,990
Alright.

144
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,870
Just don't carry that shark bag.

145
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:34,960
So, what do you want?

146
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:36,720
Be my boyfriend.

147
00:09:39,910 --> 00:09:41,480
You mean this Aunt Guan

148
00:09:41,600 --> 00:09:42,910
is threatening you with Bei?

149
00:09:46,440 --> 00:09:47,870
Then just give Bei to her.

150
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,320
He's not worth much.

151
00:09:49,570 --> 00:09:50,790
Sir, please put your feet down.

152
00:09:51,050 --> 00:09:52,240
200 yuan if you dirty the car.

153
00:09:58,270 --> 00:09:59,720
She's really scheming.

154
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,510
She'll try every way to slander my past.

155
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:04,910
That'd definitely be
beyond Bei's tolerance.

156
00:10:05,390 --> 00:10:07,360
Actually, no man would
be able to handle that.

157
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:09,510
Maybe

158
00:10:09,910 --> 00:10:11,200
someone can accept it.

159
00:10:13,720 --> 00:10:15,750
Now I get what "words can kill" means.

160
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:20,440
She called those people today, right?

161
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:21,510
Mhm.

162
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,240
She's warning me.

163
00:10:34,550 --> 00:10:35,510
Take this with you.

164
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:37,630
It might come in handy
if you're in trouble.

165
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,080
No matter how deep their love,

166
00:10:39,270 --> 00:10:41,150
they can't guard you round the clock.

167
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,670
When danger hits,
we can only rely on ourselves.

168
00:10:45,670 --> 00:10:46,510
Thanks.

169
00:10:50,000 --> 00:10:52,080
As for Aunt Guan,

170
00:10:52,960 --> 00:10:54,440
let me be the one to deal with her.

171
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,270
With a guy this perfect,

172
00:10:57,670 --> 00:10:59,390
I wanna see
what trouble she can stir up.

173
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,600
One more thing.

174
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:01,580
For real,

175
00:11:01,630 --> 00:11:03,670
I'm only here to perform,
not sell myself.

176
00:11:04,140 --> 00:11:05,080
Can you tell me

177
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:06,670
what's Bei's ex-girlfriend's name?

178
00:11:06,870 --> 00:11:08,200
Betray a friend isn't okay either.

179
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:09,300
So you're on good terms

180
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,750
with all his exes.

181
00:11:10,840 --> 00:11:12,000
Stop joking.

182
00:11:12,790 --> 00:11:15,240
I'm not close to any of his exes.

183
00:11:16,120 --> 00:11:17,480
Then it's not betraying a friend.

184
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,270
Your logic is wild.

185
00:11:22,150 --> 00:11:23,320
Tell me, please?

186
00:11:23,750 --> 00:11:24,790
I'm just curious.

187
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,790
I know nothing about Bei's past.

188
00:11:28,870 --> 00:11:29,840
If you won't tell me,

189
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,150
I'll ask someone else.

190
00:11:31,510 --> 00:11:32,550
I'll find out eventually.

191
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:33,960
Hmm.

192
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,120
Good point, you'll find out eventually.

193
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,270
But I'll never tell you.

194
00:11:38,810 --> 00:11:40,600
But if you wanna delete two words

195
00:11:40,750 --> 00:11:42,000
from the dictionary,

196
00:11:42,390 --> 00:11:43,390
I can recommend one.

197
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,840
Zhen Guan.

198
00:11:47,030 --> 00:11:48,150
His ex is Zhen Guan?

199
00:11:48,270 --> 00:11:50,390
That is the name of his shop, Sis!

200
00:11:50,510 --> 00:11:52,200
He's a workaholic.

201
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:54,270
Your rival is definitely his job.

202
00:11:58,330 --> 00:11:59,320
Which building was it again?

203
00:11:59,630 --> 00:12:01,840
Building 5, Unit 7, Room 419.

204
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,030
I left the door open for you.

205
00:12:03,200 --> 00:12:04,550
Don't leave it open. It's not safe.

206
00:12:04,910 --> 00:12:07,030
Who makes it unsafe? You?

207
00:12:07,320 --> 00:12:08,840
If I'm really in danger,

208
00:12:09,270 --> 00:12:10,480
will you come save the day?

209
00:12:10,960 --> 00:12:12,440
You haven't changed at all.

210
00:12:12,670 --> 00:12:13,670
Who says I haven't?

211
00:12:13,910 --> 00:12:15,030
I'm getting prettier.

212
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:16,440
Okay, I'm almost there.

213
00:12:18,670 --> 00:12:19,510
Here.

214
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:21,080
Are you ready?

215
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:23,200
Of course.

216
00:12:25,480 --> 00:12:27,030
I'm a pro at playing boyfriend.

217
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,670
Need any foreplay?

218
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,670
What I meant was…

219
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,630
Could you…

220
00:12:32,630 --> 00:12:34,030
Hmm? What's wrong?

221
00:12:34,030 --> 00:12:35,030
Play him.

222
00:12:38,390 --> 00:12:39,230
Him?

223
00:12:41,000 --> 00:12:42,240
I'm even better at playing him.

224
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,600
You'll see later.

225
00:12:43,910 --> 00:12:45,030
Just worried I might

226
00:12:45,030 --> 00:12:46,030
get too into it.

227
00:12:48,030 --> 00:12:48,870
Let's go.

228
00:13:38,910 --> 00:13:40,270
Our Xiaoxi

229
00:13:40,440 --> 00:13:42,240
finally has time to see me.

230
00:13:42,910 --> 00:13:43,960
I've been so busy lately.

231
00:13:44,100 --> 00:13:45,200
Today I happened to have time

232
00:13:45,320 --> 00:13:47,240
to visit you with my boyfriend.

233
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,360
This is Guan.

234
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,360
Hello, Guan, I'm…

235
00:13:51,550 --> 00:13:54,030
Young man, you're really something.

236
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:56,390
You even managed to win over Xiaoxi.

237
00:13:57,670 --> 00:13:59,750
But Xiaoxi has good taste.

238
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:01,240
After all that choosing,

239
00:14:01,840 --> 00:14:02,840
you're truly quite the catch.

240
00:14:03,000 --> 00:14:04,600
You're flattering me, Guan.

241
00:14:04,870 --> 00:14:07,080
Xiaoxi's always telling me
how amazing you are.

242
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:08,720
I should've visited you ages ago.

243
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:11,080
Seeing is believing.

244
00:14:11,270 --> 00:14:12,790
Look at Guan, she's so well-maintained.

245
00:14:13,030 --> 00:14:15,200
Don't look a day over 20,

246
00:14:15,390 --> 00:14:16,600
more like 17 or 18.

247
00:14:18,840 --> 00:14:20,030
Come on, have a seat.

248
00:14:28,510 --> 00:14:29,390
An Miu.

249
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:33,800
Where are you?

250
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:38,240
Bei, did you miss me?

251
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:40,200
Come down first.

252
00:14:41,810 --> 00:14:43,390
Can't believe it's been so long. You've…

253
00:14:44,080 --> 00:14:45,510
You've gained weight.

254
00:14:46,550 --> 00:14:47,910
Can you talk?

255
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:50,720
Would it kill you to say I got prettier?

256
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,240
Ah, fine, you're prettier.

257
00:14:52,320 --> 00:14:53,160
Happy now? Prettier.

258
00:14:53,230 --> 00:14:54,120
Too late.

259
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:55,440
Think about how to make it up to me.

260
00:14:55,630 --> 00:14:57,200
Well, I brought your favorite crawfish.

261
00:14:57,510 --> 00:14:59,030
So, what's your name, young man?

262
00:14:59,320 --> 00:15:00,240
My last name's Bao.

263
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:01,360
Given name is Bei.

264
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:03,270
You can call me Angela.

265
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,790
That name sounds pretty cool.

266
00:15:06,440 --> 00:15:07,790
Your name suits you.

267
00:15:08,910 --> 00:15:10,120
You flatter me, Guan.

268
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:13,150
My dad loved foreign classic literature.

269
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,440
When he picked my name,

270
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:16,000
he borrowed it
from a character in a book.

271
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,840
Was it Huckleberry or Isabella?

272
00:15:21,600 --> 00:15:22,840
Vegeta.

273
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:25,290
You know, the short guy

274
00:15:25,390 --> 00:15:26,790
with a receding hairline.

275
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:28,870
Back then, my dad

276
00:15:28,870 --> 00:15:30,630
probably thought I wasn't born a prince,

277
00:15:30,910 --> 00:15:33,000
but I should have the heart to
win a princess.

278
00:15:33,480 --> 00:15:34,320
Luckily,

279
00:15:34,960 --> 00:15:36,720
I didn't let him down.

280
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,910
Don't mind him, Guan.

281
00:15:47,030 --> 00:15:48,440
He just likes joking around.

282
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,750
He's pretty funny.

283
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:53,030
Where do you work now?

284
00:15:53,270 --> 00:15:54,910
Just scraping by at an appraisal shop.

285
00:15:56,000 --> 00:15:56,840
What do you appraise?

286
00:15:57,120 --> 00:15:57,960
Everything.

287
00:15:58,100 --> 00:15:59,550
Breast augmentations,
